snippet.title: Sheep with Mates - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game: https://basklein.itch.io/sheep-with-mates

The launch trailer for the game Sheep with Mates.

Sheep with Mates is a local multiplayer competitive sheep herding game for 2-8 players.

A game by basklein.
https://basklein.com/

With music by Nozem Audio.
https://nozemaudio.com/
